H. Representing, directly or by implication, that any weight loss program or services can be obtained for free, unless
respondent discloses, clearly and prominently, either (1) in close proximity to such representation, the existence
and amount of all mandatory fees associated with the free offer; or (2) in immediate conjunction with such representation,
