may involve the risk of developing serious health complications.



O. Misrepresenting, directly or by implication, the existence, contents, validity, results, conclusions, or interpretations
of any test or study.



P. Misrepresenting, directly or by implication, the performance, efficacy, or safety of any weight loss program
or weight loss product.




