1. When available, offer in-lieu lots to holders at the time that notice is given that the lot will be converted to an
alternative public use and a new permit will not be issued. If lots do not become available until later, offer them then.

2. Give first priority to identifying and offering in-lieu lots in the same tract or an expansion of that tract, where
